  "texts": [
    "With the help of online tools and resources, students can practice their writing skills in a more interactive and engaging manner.",
    "These tools provide instant feedback, which helps students identify their mistakes and improve their writing skills.Digital technology offers several benefits for writing instruction, including increased accessibility, flexibility, and interactivity.",
    "Online platforms and tools can provide students with personalized feedback, practice exercises, and resources to improve their writing skills [3].",
    "Additionally, digital technology can help students overcome language barriers by providing translation and language support [4].",
    "Some examples of digital tools and platforms that can be used for writing instruction in medical colleges include: -Grammarly: A writing assistant that checks for grammar, spelling, and punctuation errors."
